	<h1 class="h1-alt-header">
			Tips for Learning at Home		</h1>








<p>To help parents during this time of coronavirus, we have pulled together various resources and information. <strong>This tool is not designed to replace the communication, guidance and academic material provided by your school district.</strong> This is a resource guide.</p>
<h3>Overarching Advice</h3>
<ol>
<li>Keep a schedule- regularity and consistency are how children thrive.</li>
<li>Plan for downtime.</li>
<li>Find time for fun.</li>
<li>Take it a day at a time.</li>
</ol>
